# Design System

## Typography

- Font: Poppins (Google Fonts)
- Body: weight 500 (`font-medium`)
- Headings (`h1`�`h6`): weight 600 (`font-semibold`)

## Brand Colors

- Page background: `#f8f7f4`
- Panel / filter bar: `#eeece9`
- Text: `neutral-*`, `stone-*`, `emerald-*`, `amber-*`
- Selection highlight: `#d6f5e1` on `#0a0a0a`

## Tokens

- Semantic tokens in `src/styles/index.css`: `--background`, `--foreground`, `--primary`, `--radius`, etc.
- shadcn style: `radix-nova`, base color `neutral`
- Prefer shadcn CSS variables over hardcoded hex when adding new semantic colors

## UI Library

- Use shadcn/ui + Radix primitives before custom components
- Use `cn()` for class merging
- Use Lucide icons (`lucide-react`)
